Summary: This section lists the properties available for the OptionButton node.

*   action_mode (ActionMode). Default: 0 (overrides BaseButton.action_mode)
*   alignment (HorizontalAlignment). Default: 0 (overrides Button.alignment)
*   allow_reselect (bool). Default: false
*   enable_search_bar_on_item_count (int). Default: 0
*   fit_to_longest_item (bool). Default: true
*   item_count (int). Default: 0
*   popup/item_{index}/disabled (bool). Default: false
*   popup/item_{index}/icon (Texture2D).
*   popup/item_{index}/id (int). Default: 0
*   popup/item_{index}/separator (bool). Default: false
*   popup/item_{index}/text (String). Default: ""
*   selected (int). Default: -1
*   toggle_mode (bool). Default: true (overrides BaseButton.toggle_mode)
